rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey there, Rex.
That ship caught your eye?

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0003
rows.name: Yeah, I guess it's not easy to miss.

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0004
rows.name:
Never knew they made ships this big
without a Divine Beast at the core.

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0005
rows.name:
I can't even begin to imagine
how the whole thing works.

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0007
rows.name: Do you know whose ship it is?

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0008
rows.name:
Some clients of the Chairman, I think.
Don't know the details.

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0010
rows.name:
I know you're curious, but don't go
climbing on board or anything, okay?

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0012
rows.name: Anyway, I've gotta get back to work.

rows.label: fev01_070_110_msg0013
rows.name:
All right, then.
See you round, Garram!
